      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "新しい釣り竿、買った……\n磯のアイスマン・星見大五郎の限定ロッド",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bought… a new fishing rod…\nIceman of the Rocks‚ Daimaru Hoshimi's limited rod",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
