      "text": "これは一生物……大事にする\n早速メンテナンス",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is a lifelong treasure… I'll take good care of it\nTime for maintenance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5,
      "sfxList": [
