      "text": "クリーナー、つけて\nふきふきふきふき",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Applying the cleaner\nWipe‚ wipe‚ wipe‚ wipe",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！　もしかして、刀を磨く侍達も\nこんな気持ちだったのかな？　きっと愛着、あるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha! Maybe the samurai who polished their swords\nfelt this way too? They must have been so attached",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "（私は侍……私は侍……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I am a samurai… I am a samurai…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16676.798912000002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.6333422344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "数多の、剣豪の血を吸ってきた妖刀・雫丸よ。まだ血が\n吸い足らず鳴き続けるか。はぁ、最高にカッコイイ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yodo‚ Shizukumaru‚ the cursed blade that has tasted the blood of countless masters.\nDo you still thirst for more blood? Sigh‚ it's so cool…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6333422344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.0000078838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0000078838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、借りてたDVD返しに来たんだけど\n今大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ I'm here to return the DVD I borrowed\nIs now a good time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9333412171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.5666745504
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫……入って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah‚ come in…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5666745504,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2599.995676699997
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2399.9956767000012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.9666702271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "急にごめんね。声が聞こえたけどお芝居の練習だった？\n新しいDVDだから早く返そうと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for dropping by. I heard your voice—were you practicing a play?\nIt's a new DVD‚ so I wanted to get it back to you quickly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6333440145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.6333440145
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.2333419801
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、それ何？　釣りの道具？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ what's that? Fishing gear?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2333419801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.5666702272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "うん、有名な釣り師の釣り竿\n買ったから磨いてた。嬉しい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ a fishing rod from a famous angler\nJust bought it and was polishing it. I'm happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5666702272,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11133.340320700001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fishing-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16433.329772799992
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fishing-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17733.32977279999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.7000040691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ、見せて見せて！　むーん、釣り竿って\nこんなにしなるんだ！　びょーん！　びょーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ let me see‚ let me see! Wow‚ fishing rods\nbend like this! Boing! Boing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7000040691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.6666732789
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.5333465579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "さ、さくらちゃん……\nそれ、げ、限定ロッド――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sakura…\nThat's a l-limited rod—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5333465579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.4666859947
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "私、この取っ手は知ってるよ！\nこうやって回すんだよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know what this handle is!\nYou spin it like this‚ right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4666859947,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fishing-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3999.9806719999924
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.9000218712
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう。リール、糸を巻く機械……\nそれ、げ、限定――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah. The reel‚ the machine that winds the line…\nThat's a l-limited—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9000218712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.6000066122
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.2666880293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "ぐるぐるぐるぐるー！\nやったー！　釣れたー！　爆釣だー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Round and round and round!\nYay! I caught one! It's a big one!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2666880293,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fishing-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16999.984741000007
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 18699.984740999993
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.8000178023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、ごめんね雫ちゃん。なんだか\n楽しくなっちゃった。今度また釣りに連れてってね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ sorry Shizuku. I just\ngot a little carried away. Take me fishing with you next time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.8000178023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.9666809085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_04-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……ちょっと、ハラハラした……\n釣り竿は、もう少し奥にしまっておく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… that was a little nerve-wracking…\nI should keep the rod a bit further back in the room…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9666809085,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
